article.headline: N.C.-Asheville 58, Gardner-Webb 56
article.story: BOILING SPRINGS, N.C. -- Chris Stephenson's two-handed putback off the glass with 1.6 seconds left gave N.C-Asheville a 58-56 victory over Gardner-Webb on Friday night in the Big South opener for both teams. Stephenson scored all 13 of his points in the second half for Asheville (1-6). Sean Smith led the Bulldogs with 18 points. Anton Silver scored 14 points, all in the second half, for Gardner-Webb (3-3).
